WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.940
So long, since you've been at peace.

00:00:18.920 --> 00:00:24.100
You used to know how to come here... As a child.

00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:34.260
It's a place in your head.

00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:45.740
Focus on the water.

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:58.000
It's a bit of an illness to keep wanting more.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:07.760
This spot isn't glamorous...

00:01:09.460 --> 00:01:13.640
...It's what's all around, when we focus.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:25.580
This permanently exists, amidst the noise.

00:01:31.700 --> 00:01:33.680
Don't be afraid.

00:01:40.420 --> 00:01:42.020
It'll always be here...

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:44.720
...Waiting for you...

00:01:45.940 --> 00:01:48.140
... When you need it.

